 《Starfield》首席任务设计师离开贝塞斯达，与《辐射》老兵一起开发《Wyrdsong》 https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-lead-quest-designer-leaves-bethesda-to-work-on-wyrdsong-with-fallout-veterans-3516281?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign= Starfield 首席任务设计师离开贝塞斯达，与辐射退伍军人一起在 Wyrdsong 上工作Andy BrownTue, 17 Oct 2023 09:45:00 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3516281 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="维德歌。图片来源：Something Wicked Games。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “想到我们的一支团队中有来自 Bethesda、Obsidian 和 Bioware 的资深人士，真是太棒了”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-lead-quest-designer-leaves-bethesda-to-work-on-wyrdsong-with-fallout-veterans-3516281">《Starfield》后的首席任务设计师离开贝塞斯达，与《辐射》老兵一起开发《Wyrdsong》，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="维德歌。图片来源：Something Wicked Games。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Wyrdsong-will-shen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield">《Starfield》</a></em>的首席任务设计师 Will Shen 已离开<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda-softworks">Bethesda Softworks</a> ，加入<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/something-wicked-games">Something Wicked Games</a>开发其首张游戏<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/wyrdsong">《Wyrdsong》</a></em> 。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/guides/gaming-guides/best-rpg-games-2974129">2023 年您可以玩的最佳角色扮演游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p>Shen 自 2008 年开发末世射击游戏<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fallout-3">《辐射 3》</a></em>以来一直在 Bethesda 工作，此后又参与了<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-elder-scrolls-v-skyrim">《上古卷轴 5：天际》</a></em> 、 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fallout-4">《辐射 4</a></em> 》和<em>《星际争霸》</em>等游戏的制作。</p><p> Shen 的下一步是 Something Wicked Games，该公司由前 Bethesda 项目负责人 Jeff Gardiner 创立，成员包括多名<em>《辐射》</em>资深人士。该工作室目前正在开发<em>Wyrdsong</em> ，这是一款“雄心勃勃”的角色扮演游戏，已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/former-fallout-and-skyrim-developers-announce-rpg-wyrdsong-3296885">在 Gamescom 2022 上宣布</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Wyrdsong 官方预告片 |科隆游戏展 ONL 2022" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gV_oKMvSc0I?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “很高兴地宣布我加入 Something Wicked Games，”<a href="https://twitter.com/WillShen101/status/1713930817284591842" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shen 写道</a>。 “我将与一群令人难以置信的角色扮演游戏开发者一起工作，想到我们的团队中有来自 Bethesda、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/obsidian-entertainment">Obsidian</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bioware">Bioware</a>的资深人士，真是太棒了。”</p><p> Shen 在接受<a href="https://www.gamedeveloper.com/design/something-wicked-games-snaps-up-former-bethesda-lead-quest-designer-will-shen" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>游戏开发者</em></a>采访时透露，他在<em>Wyrdsong</em>中的角色将是连接 Something Wicked 的叙事和设计团队。</p><p>至于<em>《Wyrdsong》</em> ，去年，Gardiner 告诉<a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/fallout-4-and-new-vegas-veterans-team-up-to-make-new-open-world-rpg-wyrdsong/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>PC Gamer</em></a> ，这款游戏是“一款以中世纪葡萄牙为背景的黑暗、超自然、半历史的开放世界角色扮演游戏”。</p><p>此外，Gardiner 将<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a> 2022 年的热门<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">游戏《Elden Ring》</a></em>列为 Wyrdsong 的“巨大灵感”，并承认拥有如此多的前<em>《辐射》</em>开发者将产生自己的影响力。</p><p> “我认为重点在于教训，而不是<em>《辐射》</em>的背景和主题，而是这些游戏的 RPG 性质，”他分享道。 “‘有选择，有后果’说起来很容易。但我们希望确保玩家感受到我们从这些游戏中吸取的教训，即如何制作一个令人难以置信的故事，同时让玩家能够自由地在故事中做出自己的决定，并参与其中不管是不是。”</p><p> <em>Wyrdsong</em>的发布日期尚未确定，因为该游戏目前处于创建的早期阶段。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bethesdas-head-of-publishing-retires-after-24-years-with-the-developer-3515894">Bethesda 的发行主管 Pete Hines 也宣布离开</a>公司。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-lead-quest-designer-leaves-bethesda-to-work-on-wyrdsong-with-fallout-veterans-3516281">《Starfield》后的首席任务设计师离开贝塞斯达，与《辐射》老兵一起开发《Wyrdsong》，</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
